75
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:07,360
Isn't this painting of you, sister?

76
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,730
Look at her clothes,

77
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:09,590
hairpin,

78
00:04:12,670 --> 00:04:13,510
and hairstyle.

79
