152
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,440
Just do whatever you wish.

153
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:27,040
No need for excuses.

154
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,000
Don't worry about others' opinions.

155
00:07:29,350 --> 00:07:30,210
